				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				There are two Erudite staff quests that i know of.<BR>
The first is for the Peacekeeper staff, which takes<BR>
place in Erud and Qeynos.<BR>
<BR>
After you do the peacekeeper staff quest they send<BR>
you to retreive the Battlestaff, which was<BR>
supposedly stolen by someone in highpass who is<BR>
hiring mercenaries.<BR>
<BR>
I've never completed the Battlestaff quest, and <BR>
don't know if it's related to the staff pieces found<BR>
in EK.<BR>
<BR>
See the sections on Highpass or highkeep<BR>
sections for lots of speculation on what to do<BR>
with these staff parts.<BR>
