			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				 You get the High Guard BattleStaff quest form Lumi in Erudim after you finish the PeaceKeepe staff quest. She will give you a container in which you are supposed to combine the two pieces. Get the HK 401 and one first piece of the staff from the Bandit, go by the bank in HighKeep and talk to the banker. She says that she will clear out the strongbox accounts if givven the key, Give her the HK 401 and she will give you a few gold, a bit of EP and another staff piece. Combine them into the box and return them to Lumi and she will give you the High Guard BattleStaff which is: Eru, Pal, Cler only , dmg5 del 33 +10 Mana. <BR>
 NOW, I personally succesfully finished this quest but I heard that later Lumi doesn't give the box anymore and that means you can't do the quest. Ask around for more details.
				</font>
